  "mergedContent": "- Identity: Adult Companion mare, brilliant white coat, silver hooves, sapphire eyes, silver-white mane; unpartnered for three years before this\n- Arc: Drew toward devastation by the Call → found Rance collapsed in crater surrounded by wild magic residue, recognized Gift-shock and catastrophic awakening → Chose him despite age, bitterness, and destruction he caused—'There is only the right Chosen for each Companion' → rode four days/nights relentlessly to reach Haven, refused to leave his side despite exhaustion\n- Stance: [Rance] Chose him after he examined evidence; bond formed when eyes locked—mindvoice 'clear as crystal bells, warm as summer sunshine'; poured unconditional love into him, stabilized fracturing mind with mental bridges across burned channels; frustrated by stubbornness (nipped shoulder when he ignored her, insulted when called 'horse'); reciprocal affection now established; suspects his Gift rarer/more dangerous than Firestarting, unprecedented in five centuries with no one capable of training it; promised to incapacitate him if he loses control; shares his determination to warn Haven\n- Stance: [Rolan] Met Queen's Own Companion upon arrival at Haven\n- Abilities: Mind-speech with Chosen; can travel three times distance of ordinary horses; heightened magical senses",
  "canonicalName": "Senta"
}
